{"tid":2161131,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［XG01]新冠肺炎｜2度確診？　IT男4月中康復　月初遊西班牙後疑再感染","createTime":"2020-08-17T11:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:05:09.000Z","uid":189564,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"887bfd1bf9e5bb43f7c8c6685f2fb900afad0ee5","tid":2161131,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"本港疫情持續爆發，港府今（17日）延長口罩令及晚市禁堂令等安排，衛生防護中心公布，本港今新增44宗確診個案，累計增至4,525宗。其中有63人染疫的葵涌貨櫃碼頭群組，再多兩名司機確診，但並非來自連環爆疫的「宏記港務」，但「宏記」亦有一名員工初步確診。<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君又公布指，曾於3月底確診、在港從事IT的33歲男士，4月中康復後，於本月經倫敦前往西班牙旅遊，隨後返港進行檢測後，再驗出呈陽性結果，當局需再為其進行測試及基因排序分析。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a9a00ac44f14b579b7af510237b3a0b58d43ae","tid":2161131,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"條撚樣個肺仲洗唔洗要<br />\n武肺無限loop <br />\n疫苗都可能要幾個月打一次先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ecfac23c5032ab6104e2c0effb3476e357ffe6","tid":2161131,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"返閹<img src=\"